    schema1:description "After a period in the publishing industry, Henry joined the Ministry of Defence in 2000 where he undertook a range of policy, finance and HR roles. He completed an MBA in 2005 at Imperial College London before being appointed as Head of HR Policy at HM Prison Service."@en ;
